A UNIQUE HOTEL WITH TURN-OF-THE-CENTURY CHARM
Dining at our hotel - Lobby menu
Varberg Fortress
RIGHT IN THE HEART OF VARBERG ON THE WEST COAST OF SWEDEN
Boutique suite – black & gold
Varbergs Stadshotell & Asia Spa Our hotel is situated by the square in the centre of town and right by your doorstep, outside the entrance, you will find plenty of culture and shopping on offer. There is a market in that square every Wednesday and Saturday all year round. You will find the seafront just a short stroll away and a walk around the fortress is as fascinating in glorious summer sunshine as it is in blustery autumnal weather. Each season certainly has its charm and treasures in this coastal location.
The seafront promenade winds its way 2.4 kilometres from Varberg Fortress, along the seafront and all the way down to Lilla Apelviken. Enjoy the stunning scenery and salty breeze!
