How about a lovely, all-over massage in warm water measuring 30 degrees C? Make your way through the different massage stations and let the jets work their magic on your stiff muscles. For the perfect ending to your spa experience, why not visit the adjacent relaxation rooms where you can put your feet up, lie back on a day bed or chill out in a hammock chair?
POOL & SAUNA
Here you can explore and enjoy several different kinds of saunas. Eucalyptus soothes stiff joints in the steam room and the 45 degrees C heat of the salt sauna gently envelops your entire body. Try out the low-temperature sauna or cool down every now and then in our tropical rainforest shower. Right at the heart of our sauna oasis, you can cool down with a refreshing plunge in the cold tub.
