STRUGGLING TO CHOOSE THE RIGHT SPA TREATMENT?
Spa treatments and massage | Varberg | Asia Spa
Extraction (blackhead/whitehead)
If you are struggling to choose between a facial and a foot massage, we have the perfect tailor-made solution for you. You get to lie down dressed in a yukata (Japanese bathrobe) on a big, comfortable shiatzu mattress. We start with your face, you will be given acupressure, lymph drainage and massage to stimulate the warm flows in your face, neck and scalp.
BLISS - serenity
Our unique Thai massage is influenced by different methods and the overall focus is breathing, pressure and stretching. You get to lie down dressed in a yukata (Japanese bathrobe) on a large, comfortable shiatzu mattress, while our massage therapist gets to work on your muscles and joints. Oil massage is included on your legs and arms.
These treatments are based on Eastern philosophy where the focus is pressure, stretching, trigger points and inner flow. You are dressed in a yukata (bathrobe) and resting on a shiatzu mattress during your session. You can choose between the following treatments: WENLEU MASSAGE – 25 MIN, TAIYANG MASSAGE – 25 MIN or GENKI MASSAGE – 25 MIN.
Shirodhara soothes the nervous system and counteracts anxiety and sleep disorders. You also get to keep the oil that has been used during your treatment, so that you can carry on using it for oil massage in the comfort of your own home.
Scalp massage
Is your body in need of a little TLC? Why not choose a wrap, masque or scrub to both relax your mind for a few moments and cleanse your skin at the same time?
This is suitable for everyone, even mums-to-be.
The session ends with a front of body massage with delicately fragranced, warm oil. You will also be served a wholesome detox drink, which gives the benefits of this spa treatment even more depth. The detox drink is also available for purchase in our spa shop, so you can carry on your spa experience in the comfort of your own home.
You are treated to a heavenly full body massage, where the therapist uses wonderfully smooth stones for extra restorative benefits. At the same time, your body gets to rest on the same kind of smooth stones, which will invigorate you and give you new energy. A magical experience that will stay in your memory for a long time.
Skin analysis in accordance with The Five Elements
When you need to still your mind, calm your thoughts and unwind, an Indian head massage will re-energise your whole being. During this session, your head, neck and upper back will be massaged.
