Slip down into the warm water in our hot springs, explore several different kinds of saunas and enjoy a lovely all-over massage in our Vitality pool.
At long last, we are ready to welcome you as our guests to a new area for rest and recuperation at Asia Spa. On the top floor, close to the Vitality pool, you can now access our new orangery and the Surya relaxation lounge.
Start your spa experience with a Japanese ablution ritual. Scrubbing oneself is seen as a ritual where both body and soul should be cleansed. Take a seat on a wooden stool in one of our ablution rooms and allow the warm, gentle water to wash over you. Give yourself time to reflect and ponder.
”Warmth, rippling water and all the time in the world”
