Yin for sleep
Natures awe is unfolding before our very eyes every day. Even if we live in a city, mother nature still shapes our life and expresses herself constantly, we just need to learn how to connect. In this lecture you will learn in depht how to connect with nature, even when you’re not in the cabin by the lake or at a hike in the woods. You will be taught a combination of ancient and modern techniques that will allow your senses and awareness to hone in on the natural world around you. This will increase your nature connectedness in your day to day life.
