Jonna has been working as an instructor since 2003 and has used the possibilities of yoga through different phases of life. And the practice can look very different depending on what life looks like. Jonna is very appreciated in her classes for her soft voice, open empathic guidance and for keeping the room in a grounded energy.
Arrival on February 10, 11 or 12th
SEK 2,275/person
Access to about 3-5 classes and activities (depends on arrival day).
For Jonna, it is important to find the way "home". To create places and opportunities to stop and get in touch with oneself and increase awareness of the inner life. This shines through during al styles of Jonna's classes. You are guided to be present in your body and listen to yourself. The inner teacher is a cornerstone of Jonna's instructorship.
Yoga has helped Karolin both physically and mentally and she therefore chose to become a yoga teacher so she could inspire others. She traveled to Bali and did her yoga teacher training there at one of Bali's older yoga schools - Shades of Yoga (RYT200 Yoga Alliance).
